metadata.name: Crash Landed #1
metadata.description:
Created from 2013 to 2021, these images are part of a photo series called Crash Landed.

⁠The series depicts an astronaut returning to Earth, which has been destroyed and abandoned by humans. While the images are surreal and cinematic, they also evoke a very human feeling of isolation - a feeling we all are very familiar with after Covid-19.⁠

Edition 1/1 by Ken Hermann
